      <title>美联储巴尔将在行业阻力和监管延迟后公布巴塞尔计划</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/feds-barr-unveil-basel-plan-after-industry-pushback-regulatory-delays-2024-09-10/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储监管负责人将于周二概述官员们计划如何推进巴塞尔协议终局银行资本增加，此前激烈的行业反对导致该项目被推迟，并引发了联邦银行业监管机构高层之间的分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/feds-barr-unveil-basel-plan-after-industry-pushback-regulatory-delays-2024-09-10/</guid>
